<p source="SHANGBO.ZIGAO 2.5.1 (STRIP 1) JI XUSHENG 2: 25-26"><pb xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-1a" ed="tls" n="001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-1a.1">[...] 有虞氏之樂正質夔(?)之子也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-1a.2">子羔曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-1a.3">何故以得為帝?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-1a.4">孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-1a.5">"昔者而弗世也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-1a.6">善與善相受也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-1a.7">故能治天下,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-1a.8">平萬邦,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-1a.9">使亡有</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-1a.10">少大</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-1a.11">肥脆</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-1a.12">使諧得其社稷</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-1a.13">百姓而奉守之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-1a.14">堯見舜之德賢,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-1a.15">故讓之."</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZIGAO 2.5.2 (STRIPS 1-3) JI XUSHENG 2: 26"><pb xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-2a" ed="tls" n="001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-2a.1">子羔曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-2a.2">堯之得舜也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-2a.3">舜之德則誠善(2) 歟?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-2a.4">抑堯之德則甚明歟?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-2a.5">孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-2a.6">均也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-2a.7">舜穡於童土之田, 則 [...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-2a.8">[...] 之童土之黎民也.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZIGAO 2.5.3 (STRIPS 3-5) JI XUSHENG 2: 26"><pb xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-3a" ed="tls" n="001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-3a.1">孔子曰 [...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-3a.2">吾聞[夫舜之幼也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-3a.3">敏以[孝?]侍其親](?):</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-3a.4">[...] 或以憫(?)而遠.[...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-3a.5">堯之取舜也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-3a.6">從諸卉茅之中,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-3a.7">與之言禮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-3a.8">悅薄 (?) [...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZIGAO 2.5.4 (STRIP 7+14) JI XUSHENG 2: 26"><pb xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-4a" ed="tls" n="001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-4a.1">[...] 亦紀(?). [...] (?).</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-4a.2">先王之遊,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-4a.3">道不逢廢(?),</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-4a.4">王則亦不大變(?).</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-4a.5">孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-4a.6">舜其可謂受命之民矣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-4a.7">舜,人子也[...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-4a.8">[...] 參天子事之. [...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZIGAO 2.5.5 (STRIP 8) JI XUSHENG 2: 26"><pb xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-5a" ed="tls" n="001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-5a.1">[...] X 而和,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-5a.2">故夫舜之德其誠賢矣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-5a.3">抽諸畎畝之中,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-5a.4">而使君天下</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-5a.5">而稱.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-5a.6">子羔曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-5a.7">如舜在今之世</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-5a.8">則何若?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-5a.9">孔子曰:[...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZIGAO 2.5.6 (STRIP 9) JI XUSHENG 2: 26"><pb xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-6a" ed="tls" n="001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-6a.1">子羔問於孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-6a.2">參王者之作也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-6a.3">皆人子也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-6a.4">而其父賤</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-6a.5">而不足偁也歟?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-6a.6">抑亦誠天子也歟?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-6a.7">孔子曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-6a.8">善,爾問之也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-6a.9">久矣, 其莫 [...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZIGAO 2.5.7 (STRIPS 11A+10) JI XUSHENG 2: 26"><pb xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-7a" ed="tls" n="001-7a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-7a.1">[禹之母有莘氏之女] 也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-7a.2">觀於伊</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-7a.3">而得之</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-7a.4">懷三年</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-7a.5">而劃於背而生,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-7a.6">生而能言,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-7a.7">是禹也.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZIGAO 2.5.8 (STRIPS 10+11B+CUBS3+12) JI XUSHENG 2: 26"><pb xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-8a" ed="tls" n="001-8a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-8a.1">契之母有娀氏之女也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-8a.2">遊於陽臺之上,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-8a.3">有燕銜卵</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-8a.4">而措諸其前,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-8a.5">取而吞之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-8a.6">娠三年而劃於膺,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-8a.7">生而呼曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-8a.8">「欽!」   “</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-8a.9">是契也.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZIGAO 2.5.9 (STRIPS 12-13) JI XUSHENG 2: 27"><pb xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-9a" ed="tls" n="001-9a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-9a.1">后稷之母有邰氏之女也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-9a.2">遊於玄丘之內,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-9a.3">冬見芺,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-9a.4">搴而薦之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-9a.5">乃見人武,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-9a.6">履以祈禱曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-9a.7">"帝之武,尚使 [...].</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-9a.8">是后稷(之母)也.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.ZIGAO 2.5.10 (STRIP 13) JI XUSHENG 2: 27"><pb xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-10a" ed="tls" n="001-10a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-10a.1">參王者之作也如是.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-10a.2">子羔曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0036_tls_001-10a.3">“然則參王者孰為〔...〕</seg></p>

